    "text": "This translation key is used to describe the \"Disable SSL\" option on a settings page, likely a button or toggle that disables Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) verification. Its purpose is to inform users about the consequences of this action and provide context for developers. It appears in the Portal Settings category.",
